Utterance.UttText: In bed 4 is Belinda da Silva, 33 yrs old under Dr Mepua.
She had tummy flu a week ago and was vomiting and now diagnosed with lung infection.
She is a new admission and her blood results just came in today and it hasn't been reviewed by the doctors yet.
She is on IV antibiotics bd and puffers prn.
Otherwise, the patient is self caring and ambulant and no urgent issues noted.
